name: Amaranth bracelet  No.04
description:
A unique, handmade bracelet. 
It's a mix of all cultures with a piece of all continents.
Made from leather, colorfast cotton and a special button.
Size: 17 cm, if you want another size, smaller or bigger, please contact me. I will make it for you. 

Can be worn alone and I also love to wear more bracelets, layered with others.

No. 04 is a bracelet with broken white, army green and purple cotton with a special button.

Handmade with love.


Wil je per bankoverschrijving betalen? Dat kan. Neem contact met me op, dan stuur ik je mijn rekeningnummer.
